体形状，②____________________。他引述孔子之语，把&ldquo;天圆地方&rdquo;说成是&ldquo;天道曰圆，地道曰方&rdquo;，即天所遵循的规律在性质上属于&ldquo;圆&rdquo;，转动不休；地所遵循的规律在性质上则属于&ldquo;方&rdquo;，安谧静止。③____________________，固然可以弥补&ldquo;天圆地方&rdquo;说在形式上的缺陷，但这种修补却也使该说丧失了作为一种宇宙结构学说而存在的资格，因为它所谈论的已经不再是天地的具体形状了。</p>","createBy":"35988","createName":null,"createTime":"2023-01-05T09:16:09","decipherment":null,"deleted":false,"difficultyId":null,"difficultyName":null,"gradeId":null,"id":"817566191928217837","isCharged":false,"isGroupQuestion":true,"isSubjective":false,"lineNumber":1,"oldId":null,"optionA":null,"optionB":null,"optionC":null,"optionD":null,"optionE":null,"optionF":null,"optionG":null,"options":[],"origin":1,"paperTypeId":null,"parentId":"0","pickCount":0,"provinceId":null,"questionNumber":null,"questionSerialNo":3462048,"questionVideo":null,"relateKnowledge":null,"scoreBasis":null,"source":null,"title":null,"typeDetailId":"6","typeDetailName":"简答题","typeId":"10","typeName":"语言文字运用","updateBy":"35988","updateName":null,"updateTime":"2023-01-05T09:16:09","uploadBatch":"1672881369744","yearId":null},"questionId":null,"questionNumber":null}],"title":""}],"templateId":"170208","templateName":"第四单元　单元综合检测"},"msg":null}